<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Your <%= @plan.capitalize %> plan is active!</h2>

  <p>Hi <%= @manager.email_address %>,</p>

  <p>Great news — your <strong><%= @plan.capitalize %></strong> subscription for <strong><%= @account.name %></strong> is now active.</p>

  <% case @plan %>
  <% when "starter" %>
    <p>You now have access to up to <strong>10 projects</strong>.</p>
  <% when "pro" %>
    <p>You now have <strong>unlimited projects</strong>. No limits!</p>
  <% end %>

  <p>You can manage your subscription any time from your <%= link_to "Billing page", billing_url %>.</p>

  <p>Thanks for supporting CrewControl!</p>

  <p>— The CrewControl Team</p>
</body>
</html>
